service.tut.pori.contentanalysis.video

Class VideoList

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.tut.pori.http.ResponseData
      • service.tut.pori.contentanalysis.video.VideoList
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DeletedVideoList

    public class VideoList
extends ResponseData
    This is a container class for video elements, which can be used directly with Response to provide XML output.

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<mediaList>
  <media>
    <credits>SFqBzNJOhylLSYMjiECBNYaSbkQllBPZEMKoWQWNnzsTLdVqhkKbQiEgAcChvIlI</credits>
    <description>ohJQtbqPqDzHjdCuZczJAXdAGhfAUWnyZJEbnEMwHWbPwCeyffUTPJuSywmDBPBk</description>
    <UID>19829292-ef89-416f-960f-b1d7b11e34fd</UID>
    <name>cugsioiebeBllIwEvFrTCLMDQFecwHSfUvOxxrnUOLXPbvDwztOgxMhQhIAFaulo</name>
    <serviceId>1</serviceId>
    <visibility>PUBLIC</visibility>
    <objectList>
      <object>
        <backendId>123140383</backendId>
        <confidence>0.7635220083362054</confidence>
        <mediaObjectId>4589843724442898034</mediaObjectId>
        <mediaType>VIDEO</mediaType>
        <objectId>XUvwLwTZXLnaOmACvzTKJTvljniZgHttFZESRXMAfZhzpcBpiCNmWpmCcQNngnYF</objectId>
        <rank>788949782</rank>
        <serviceId>1</serviceId>
        <status>CANDIDATE</status>
        <objectType>KEYWORD</objectType>
        <value>jpMekJkpjElhzlJUMSRRazpvilVoYYWeUxEdRDatfCMUgPzcdMkZeRwZOBDSytLb</value>
        <visibility>PRIVATE</visibility>
        <timeCodeList>
          <timeCode>
            <to>2423.2684506283576</to>
            <from>1768.3926772437492</from>
          </timeCode>
        </timeCodeList>
        <userId>4966512143658566987</userId>
      </object>
    </objectList>
    <mediaType>VIDEO</mediaType>
    <userId>4966512143658566987</userId>
    <url>http://fe.example.org/rest/vcarc/r?uid=19829292-ef89-416f-960f-b1d7b11e34fd&amp;service_id=1</url>
  </media>
</mediaList>
